832
01:07:13,944 --> 01:07:16,404
- It'll have to wait.
- No. This won't wait.

833
01:07:16,488 --> 01:07:20,992
When the 9.1 2 from Toronto landed, they
found four prescriptions without an MPL.

834
01:07:21,076 --> 01:07:23,745
They tried to take the pills away
and he went nuts.

835
01:07:23,828 --> 01:07:26,498
There he is.
We think they're for his father.

836
