- Russia.

840
01:07:38,677 --> 01:07:41,304
The only interpreter
we got is in Newark.

841
01:07:41,388 --> 01:07:45,058
- We have to get someone to talk to him.
- I have an idea, sir.

842
01:07:48,687 --> 01:07:50,689
Viktor.

843
01:07:51,398 --> 01:07:53,441
Viktor.

844
01:07:53,525 --> 01:07:56,111
Oh...

845
01:07:56,194 --> 01:07:58,113
I need your help.

846
01:07:59,281 --> 01:08:02,200
His name is Milodragovich.
He lives near you.

847
01:08:02,284 --> 01:08:04,077
He may not speak your dialect,

848
01:08:04,160 --> 01:08:06,580
but I need you to translate
and help me out.

849
01:08:06,621 --> 01:08:09,499
- I help you? Why?
- I don't want anybody to get hurt.

850
01:08:09,583 --> 01:08:10,959
This guy's very upset.

851
