865
01:09:40,423 --> 01:09:45,387
His plane landed in the US.
He needs to have the right form.

866
01:09:57,315 --> 01:09:59,651
He did not know
he need this document.

867
01:09:59,734 --> 01:10:01,903
No one say to him
he need document form.

868
01:10:01,987 --> 01:10:03,280
I'm saying it to him.

869
01:10:03,363 --> 01:10:08,827
He needs to have the form signed by
the hospital who is treating his father.

870
01:10:08,910 --> 01:10:11,997
These medicines
have to stay in the United States.

871
01:10:12,080 --> 01:10:13,415
They have to stay here.

872
01:10:30,849 --> 01:10:33,894
