873
01:10:33,977 --> 01:10:36,438
I know. I can see that he's begging.

874
01:10:40,650 --> 01:10:42,110
I'm sorry, sir.

875
01:10:43,320 --> 01:10:48,450
You'll have to take a flight in the
morning. The medicine stays here.

876
01:10:49,618 --> 01:10:51,578
I'm sorry.

877
01:10:55,165 --> 01:10:57,000
Send him down!

878
01:11:02,339 --> 01:11:05,133
Thank you, Viktor.
