893
01:12:08,029 --> 01:12:09,614
- No, it's not.
- Yes.

894
01:12:09,698 --> 01:12:11,575
- No.
- Yes.

895
01:12:11,658 --> 01:12:13,869
You read the blue immigration form.

896
01:12:13,952 --> 01:12:14,995
- Blue?
- Yes. Blue.

897
01:12:15,078 --> 01:12:16,997
- Blue?
- Blue. The blue form.

898
01:12:17,080 --> 01:12:20,750
The one that says if it's an animal,
he doesn't need the license.

899
01:12:20,834 --> 01:12:25,005
Then he can bring the drugs in.
That's good, Viktor. That's very good.

900
01:12:26,882 --> 01:12:29,467
Why are you doing this? Huh?

901
01:12:29,593 --> 01:12:32,554
You don't know him.
You don't know the rules.

902
01:12:32,637 --> 01:12:34,973
Look at me.

903
01:12:35,056 --> 01:12:37,017
I was going to help you.

904
01:12:38,768 --> 01:12:42,731
Now I want you to ask him...
No, not you.

905
01:12:42,814 --> 01:12:45,775
I want you to ask him.
I want to hear him say it.

906
01:12:45,817 --> 01:12:49,905
I want to hear him say
who the medicine is for.

907
01:12:49,946 --> 01:12:52,949
Please. Who the medicine is for.

908
01:13:02,792 --> 01:13:07,047
Answer him, Mr. Milodragovich.
Who are the pills for?

909
01:13:13,762 --> 01:13:17,098
OK. The pills stay. He goes. That's it.

910
01:13:22,312 --> 01:13:24,272
Goat.

911
01:13:25,023 --> 01:13:27,692
Please. For goat.

912
01:13:27,776 --> 01:13:30,028
Medicine for goat.

913
01:13:30,111 --> 01:13:32,739
Medicine for goat.

914
01:13:32,822 --> 01:13:34,699
Medicine for goat.

