He can hide inside and we'll drive out.

966
01:18:29,703 --> 01:18:33,832
- No. I can't do this.
- You said you wanted us to help you.

967
01:18:33,915 --> 01:18:36,042
- I do.
- What's her name?

968
01:18:36,126 --> 01:18:37,419
Amelia Warren.

969
01:18:37,544 --> 01:18:40,380
I thought we were looking
for a way out, not a way in.

970
01:18:40,422 --> 01:18:44,050
Be careful. Those flight attendants
ain't like regular women.

971
01:18:44,092 --> 01:18:48,430
